# Normalize line endings to LF on every platform.
#
# The CLAN golden tests byte-compare chatter's program output (always LF) against
# committed `.clan.txt` golden files. On Windows, git's autocrlf default checks
# those files out with CRLF, so every byte-match golden test failed on the
# windows-latest cross-platform leg. Forcing LF on checkout fixes it; `text=auto`
# lets git leave genuinely binary files untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf
